Water Street at the S.W. corner of James Slip. Also shown is James Slip, at and adjoining the S.W. corner of Water Street. The corner building is a frame house. (Direction of Water Street is arbitrarily set to run east and west from the Brooklyn Bridge to East Street).

March 5, 1923.

Gift of E. M. Jenks.
